# Hacker News top stories ids

Retrieves top stories ids using Hacker News API

## Usage

``` r
get_top_stories_ids()
```

## Value

list of top stories ids

## Examples

``` r
# \donttest{
# retrieve the ids of current top stories on Hacker News
top_stories_ids <- get_top_stories_ids()
```
